        Same-Day Restaurant Exhaust Fan Parts &amp; <span class="text-[#FF5E15]">Professional Installation</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mb-8 reveal-child">
        Replacement part or new system? We source it, verify fit, and install it — often same day.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-10 reveal-child">
        <a href={`tel:${business.phoneRaw}`} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#032C5B] text-white font-heading font-semibold rounded hover:scale-95 transition-transform duration-150">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M164.9 24.6c-7.7-18.6-28-28.5-47.4-23.2l-88 24C12.1 30.2 0 46 0 64C0 311.4 200.6 512 448 512c18 0 33.8-12.1 38.6-29.5l24-88c5.3-19.4-4.6-39.7-23.2-47.4l-96-40c-16.3-6.8-35.2-2.1-46.3 11.6L304.7 368C234.3 334.7 177.3 277.7 144 207.3L193.3 167c13.7-11.2 18.4-30 11.6-46.3l-40-96z"/></svg>
